  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Refactor tcp by @Ozoniuss in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/749\r\n* Add receiving on Linux and classic mode to README by @clemisch in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/753\r\n* croc --classic Yes/no prompt default is backwards by @schollz in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/761\r\n* define relay ports by amount by @tnothy in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/763\r\n* prevent error message before insstalling completion file for non root user by @doc75 in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/762\r\n* fix test case name by @tnothy in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/766\r\n* fix upload speed throttling by @tnothy in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/767\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @Ozoniuss made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/749\r\n* @clemisch made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/753\r\n* @tnothy made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/763\r\n* @doc75 made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/762\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/schollz/croc/compare/v10.0.10...v10.0.11",
